						               													<description>Norsgard; is a tabletop wargame set in the cold realm of Isbran - a land of ice and fire.  The players in this game play out the skirmishes of small bands of warriors led into battle by heroes.&amp;#10; &amp;quot;During the game the situation changes rapidly - until you have secured your victory, you can never be sure of it. React to your opponents actions, block their charges, and keep them from blocking yours at the crucial moment. Play Special Cards to turn the tide of battle to give yourself the advantage and when combat commences, choose the right Tactic and push your enemies onto the defensive. From turn to turn build your dominance and win combats so that the initiative stays with you. Press your opponent until you reach your goals. Together, create an epic battle in which every warrior plays their part!&amp;#10;&amp;#10; &amp;#10;&amp;quot;Never again will you have to depend on a single dice roll - in this game you literally roll a handful. Watch as they shape the fate of your warriors and thanks to simple, easy-to-learn mechanics you will be able to concentrate on your strategy instead of trying to remember an obscure rules technicality.&amp;#10; &amp;quot;Create your own saga, direct your heroes, and influence their future. In many cases the players will decide the fate of their characters; in big tournaments and during fierce battles they may acquire legendary artifacts or gain experience - become a great leader, a fearsome warrior - or they may perish... Norsgard awaits it's heroes, and always remember:&amp;#10; Fortune favours the bold!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
